<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>140</hymn_number>
<title>HE RELEASED US FROM OUR BONDAGE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Puipa mimbang a pieng tai,
 Hallelujah!
 Henkawl nang bang ei sut tai,
 Hallelujah!
 Ei di'n hinna a tung tai,
 Hallelujah!
 Gitloh teutui bang a thieng,
 Hallelujah!

[V2]
 2. Henkawl nang bang ei sut tai,
 Hallelujah!
 Thihna gui ei phelsak tai,
 Hallelujah!
 Tichun, hin tui bang a luong,
 Hallelujah!
 Zinmang suohmai a ngui hi,
 Hallelujah!

[V3]
 3. Gitloh leibat cheng A din,
 Hallelujah!
 Amah chuh lambang pak hitiu,
 Hallelujah!
 Thangvan khaw lunlui a chun,
 Hallelujah!
 Ngaihluot cheng tui bang gawmding,
 Hallelujah!

[V4]
 4. Zuo Vawnchawih tunin A pieng,
 Hallelujah!
 Zingdawng Sawl No a suok ie,
 Hallelujah!
 Nawpna zaila lel hitiu,
 Hallelujah!
 Leisiet, thangvana Lalpen,
 Hallelujah!</lyrics>
</song>